'''卡氏間質細胞'''（interstitial cell of Cajal、ICC，卡哈爾細胞）是在[[胃腸道|胃腸道]]中發現的一種[[間質細胞|間質細胞]]。有不同類型且具有不同的功能。其中「肌間質細胞」（Myenteric Interstitial cells of Cajal [ICC-MY] ）作為起搏器產生[[慢波電位|慢波電位]](slow wave potential)，能導致平滑肌的收縮。<ref name="pmid20059699">{{cite journal |vauthors=Hennig GW, Spencer NJ, Jokela-Willis S, Bayguinov PO, Lee HT, Ritchie LA, Ward SM, Smith TK, Sanders KM | title = ICC-MY coordinate smooth muscle electrical and mechanical activity in the murine small intestine | journal = Neurogastroenterol. Motil. | volume = 22 | issue = 5 | pages = e138–51 |date=May 2010  | pmid = 20059699 | pmc = 2856807 | doi = 10.1111/j.1365-2982.2009.01448.x | url = }}</ref><ref name=Sanders>{{cite journal |vauthors=Sanders K, Koh S, Ward S |title=Interstitial cells of cajal as pacemakers in the gastrointestinal tract |journal=Annu Rev Physiol |volume=68 |issue= |pages=307–343 |year= 2006|pmid=16460275 |doi=10.1146/annurev.physiol.68.040504.094718}}</ref>

另一種，"肌內卡氏間質細胞"(Intramuscular Interstitial cells of Cajal [[ICC-IM|ICC-IM]])參與平滑肌細胞的激活，通過它們進行神經遞質作用。<ref name="pmid21757854">{{cite journal | author = Kito Y | title = The functional role of intramuscular interstitial cells of Cajal in the stomach | journal = J Smooth Muscle Res | volume = 47 | issue = 2 | pages = 47–53 | year = 2011 | pmid = 21757854 | doi = 10.1540/jsmr.47.47| url = }}</ref>某些[[鈣激活氯通道|鈣激活氯通道]](calcium-activated chloride channels (CaCCs))現在已知在調節人體胃腸的ICC中發揮重要的作用，特別是在鈣激活氯通道[[ANO1|ANO1]]。<ref name="ICC review" />最近的一篇評論指出，[[卡巴膽鹼|卡巴膽鹼]](carbachol)通過這一通道來增加ICC的活動。<ref name="ICC review">{{cite journal |vauthors=Sanders KM, Zhu MH, Britton F, Koh SD, Ward SM | title = Anoctamins and gastrointestinal smooth muscle excitability | journal = Exp. Physiol. | volume = 97 | issue = 2 | pages = 200–206 |date=February 2012  | pmid = 22002868 | pmc = 3272164 | doi = 10.1113/expphysiol.2011.058248 | url = }}</ref><ref name="pmid21768263">{{cite journal |vauthors=Zhu MH, Sung IK, Zheng H, Sung TS, Britton FC, O'Driscoll K, Koh SD, Sanders KM | title = Muscarinic activation of Ca2+-activated Cl- current in interstitial cells of Cajal | journal = J. Physiol. (Lond.) | volume = 589 | issue = Pt 18 | pages = 4565–82 |date=September 2011  | pmid = 21768263 | pmc = 3208225 | doi = 10.1113/jphysiol.2011.211094 | url = }}</ref>"敲除ANO1基因"(ANO1-knockout)的老鼠不能在人體產生慢波及ANO1通道抑製劑來阻斷慢波的產生。<ref name="ICC review" />

許多類型的平滑肌組織現已證明含有ICC，但除了少數例外的細胞且這些例外的細胞功能還是是未知的；故而目前這是一個很活躍的[[研究|研究]]領域。

而卡氏間質細胞衍自[[中胚层|中胚层]]。<ref name="Turksen2006">{{cite book|author=Kursad Turksen|title=Embryonic Stem Cell Protocols: Differentiation models|url=http://books.google.com/?id=9Wk-5wuIR5gC&pg=PA263|accessdate=14 April 2010|year=2006|publisher=Humana Press|isbn=978-1-58829-784-6|pages=263–}}</ref>

==慢波活動的作用==
ICC作為[[電|電子]]心臟起搏器，及在[[胃腸道|胃腸道]](gastrointestinal tract)產生自發性的[[慢波電位|慢波電位]](slow wave potential)。<!--Electrical slow waves spread from ICC to [[smooth_muscle_cell|smooth muscle cell]]s and the resulting depolarization initiates [[calcium_ion|calcium ion]] entry and contraction.  Slow waves organize gut contractions into phasic contractions that are the basis for [[peristalsis|peristalsis]] and [[segmentation_contractions|segmentation]].{{medical citation needed|date=March 2014}}
-->

==ICC起搏細胞的頻率==
ICC起搏器活動的頻率不同在胃腸道的不同區域之情況：<ref>Pocock, Richards, Richards, Human Physiology 4/ed, Oxford University Press, 2012. ISBN 978-0-19-957493-3. p.581</ref>
<!--* 3 per minute in the [[stomach|stomach]]
* 11-12 per minute in the [[duodenum|duodenum]]
* 9-10 per minute in the [[ileum|ileum]]
* 3-4 per minute in the [[Colon_(anatomy)|colon]]

ICC also mediate neural input from [[bowels|enteric]] [[motor_neuron|motor neuron]]s. Animals lacking ICC have greatly reduced responses to the [[neurotransmitter|neurotransmitter]] [[acetylcholine|acetylcholine]], released from excitatory motor neurons, and to the [[cell_signaling|transmitter]] [[nitric_oxide|nitric oxide]], released from [[inhibitory_motor_neuron|inhibitory motor neuron]]s. Loss of ICC in [[disease|disease]], therefore, may interrupt normal neural control of gastrointestinal (GI) contractions and lead to [[functional_GI_disorder|functional GI disorder]]s, such as [[irritable_bowel_syndrome|irritable bowel syndrome]].{{medical citation needed|date=March 2014}}

ICC also express mechano-sensitive mechanisms that cause these cells to respond to stretch. Stretching GI muscles can affect the [[resting_potential|resting potential]]s of ICC and affect the frequency of pacemaker activity.  [[Carbachol|Carbachol]] increases ICC activity through [[ANO1|ANO1]] activation.<ref name="ICC review" /><ref name="pmid21768263" />

ICC are also critical in the propagation of electrical slow waves.  ICC form a network through which slow wave activity can propagate. If this network is broken, then 2 regions of muscle will function independently.{{medical citation needed|date=March 2014}}
-->

==病理==
ICC 被認為是從[[胃腸道基質腫瘤|胃腸道基質腫瘤]](GISTs)所產生的細胞。<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Miettinen M, Lasota J |title=Gastrointestinal stromal tumors: review on morphology, molecular pathology, prognosis, and differential diagnosis |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_archives-of-pathology-laboratory-medicine_2006-10_130_10/page/1466 |journal=Arch Pathol Lab Med |volume=130 |issue=10 |pages=1466–78 |year=2006 |pmid=17090188 |doi=10.1043/1543-2165(2006)130[1466:GSTROM]2.0.CO;2 |issn=1543-2165}}</ref><!--Also, abnormalities in the ICC network is one cause of [[chronic_intestinal_pseudo-obstruction|chronic intestinal pseudo-obstruction]].<ref name=degiorgio>{{cite journal |vauthors=De Giorgio R, Sarnelli G, Corinaldesi R, Stanghellini V |title=Advances in our understanding of the pathology of chronic intestinal pseudo-obstruction |journal=Gut |volume=53 |issue=11 |pages=1549–1552 |year=2004 |pmid=15479666 |doi=10.1136/gut.2004.043968 |pmc=1774265}} [http://gut.bmjjournals.com/cgi/content/full/53/11/1549 Full Text]</ref>
-->

==命名==
卡氏間質細胞是以[[圣地亚哥·拉蒙-卡哈尔|圣地亚哥·拉蒙-卡哈尔]]來命名的，<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Sanders K, Ward S |title=Interstitial cells of Cajal: a new perspective on smooth muscle function |journal=J Physiol |volume=576 |issue=Pt 3 |pages=721–726 |year=2006 |pmid=16873406 |doi=10.1113/jphysiol.2006.115279 |pmc=1890422}}</ref>"聖地亞哥·拉蒙 - 卡哈爾"他是一位[[西班牙人|西班牙籍]]的病理學家以及[[诺贝尔生理学或医学奖|诺贝尔生理学或医学奖]]的得主。

